data.description: This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence is the epitome of modern comfort and convenience, with an added bonus den that can effortlessly transform into a 4th bedroom or serve as the perfect home office.As you step inside, the warm embrace of wood plank floors welcomes you, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere throughout. The heart of this home is its recently upgraded kitchen featuring sleek granite countertops and state-of-the-art, smart appliances. This residence boasts not only style but practicality, with a roof that's just 3 years old and recently replaced A/C just 2 years ago, offering peace of mind and minimizing future maintenance concerns.
